      <title>Bison Week: VIP Meet and Greet - Bison Panel at Blackburn Center (Armour J. Blackburn University Center)</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/53443895264525/huge/f2f9d38fb8c6a31d25152579be439d4d90cf3771.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Mon, 10 Aug 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>The Bison Week Bison Panel is designed to allow students to meet various student leaders on Campus through a moderated panel and audience questions in rotating hour-long sessions (4 sessions). During intermissions, students will be asked various Howard trivia questions and entered into raffles to win Baby Bison Baskets, as well as dance battles, and finish the lyric to increase crowd engagement.</p>

<p> </p>

<p>Each panel will have a mix of student leaders from the HU Royal Court, Senate, School Councils, Howard University Student Association, Judiciary, and Elections Commission.</p>

